    public static class MailMessage.SentDateComparator<T extends MailMessage>
extends BasicStorable.CdateComparator<T>
    Compares two MailMessage using their SentDate in descending order (newest date first). Default to Cdate Comparison if the 2 SentDate are the equals. Note: this comparator imposes orderings that are inconsistent with equals.
    See Also:
    BasicStorable.CdateComparator
